Hey, Lois, do we need
any jeans milk at home?

12:40.669 --> 12:43.170
Oh, hey, Connie.
Nice shopping outfit.

12:43.171 --> 12:44.455
Come on, Connie.

12:44.456 --> 12:46.081
It's the only brand I use.

12:46.082 --> 12:49.343
I need it to pat down bacon
and let Meg suck the wad.

12:49.344 --> 12:50.794
Too bad, bitch.

12:50.795 --> 12:52.729
(scanner beeps)

